<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EduHustlr | Lo-Fi Vibe</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #000;
            --text: #fff;
            --accent: #888;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 700px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            letter-spacing: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--text);
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .recommendations {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .recommendations li {
            border: 1px solid #333;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .recommendations li:hover {
            border-color: var(--text);
            background: #111;
        }

        .recommendations a {
            color: var(--text);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
        }

        .tagline {
            text-align: center;
            font-style: italic;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .back-home {
            margin-top: 60px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--accent);
            border: 1px solid var(--accent);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .back-home:hover {
            color: var(--text);
            border-color: var(--text);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>LO-FI</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>01. The Definition</h2>
            <p>
                Short for <strong>low-fidelity</strong>, Lo-Fi is a music aesthetic that embraces imperfections. 
                Where modern pop chases polished perfection, Lo-Fi finds beauty in the cracks—the hiss of a vinyl record, 
                the hum of a tape deck, and the soft "mistakes" of a live performance.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>02. The Vibe</h2>
            <p>
                It is the sound of a rainy Tuesday evening. It's the companion to a late-night study session or a 
                solitary walk through a quiet city. It’s designed not to take center stage, but to create a "headspace" 
                where your mind can wander or focus.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>03. Where to Listen</h2>
            <ul class="recommendations">
                <li>
                    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jfKfPfyJRdk" target="_blank">Lofi Girl (YouTube)</a>
                    <span>The gold standard of the genre. 24/7 beats to study/relax to.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DWWQRv9pS0v3z" target="_blank">Lo-Fi Beats (Spotify)</a>
                    <span>A curated selection of the most iconic chill-hop tracks.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://soundcloud.com/chilledcow" target="_blank">ChilledCow (SoundCloud)</a>
                    <span>Great for finding underground artists and new sounds.</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="tagline">Stay chill. Keep hustling.</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="index.html" class="back-home">RETURN TO HUB</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
